Class AeDefPathParallelVisitor

All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeDefPathVisitor, IAeDefVisitor
Direct Known Subclasses:
AeImplPathParallelVisitor
public class AeDefPathParallelVisitor
extends AeDefPathVisitor

Extension of the location path visitor that creates a custom path for the root scope of the forEach. All of the other nodes visited will get their standard path which will include the scope's special instance predicate which serves to make the paths unique.
